686→\section{Experimental methodology}
687→\label{sec:methodology}
688→
689→This section describes the experimental design used to evaluate the four pillars of the proposed system: hallucination reduction, token economy, processing speed, and security. We define baselines (Section~\ref{sec:baselines}), metrics (Section~\ref{sec:metrics}), datasets (Section~\ref{sec:datasets}), and the evaluation protocol (Section~\ref{sec:protocol}).
690→
691→\subsection{Baselines}
692→\label{sec:baselines}
693→
694→We compare the proposed multi-strategy GraphRAG system against four baselines, summarized in Table~\ref{tab:baselines}.
