706→MS GraphRAG & Microsoft GraphRAG \citep{edge2024graphrag} with Leiden community detection and global summarization. No security model or intent-aware fusion. \\
707→HybridRAG & Graph + vector retrieval without community detection \citep{sarmah2024hybridrag}. Combines two retrieval strategies with equal weights. \\
